or a revenue-focused user", "number": "103"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-13", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Auto-Enable Omni Channel when Digital Engagement is set up", "number": "104"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-13", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Continuous Conversation in Omni Inbox for a Seller", "number": "105"}], "name": "[264] Routing for Sales"}], "subcloud": "FY27 SC M10 UACP", "target_release": "264", "theme": "\u26ab Not Prioritized"}, {"health": "On Track", "health_comments": "27-May: Teams aligned on Go-live date 5/28 but is conditional on resolving two launch-blocking voice/text mode switch bugs and completing the Edge rollout. Live Transcription (Streaming): scrt2-chatbot and voice worker changes ready, but streaming tokens to MIAW have a gap upstream \u2014 under active debugging. June 8 deadline is the target. ECv2 Voice in 262: Changes now available in build 262; 264 integration is WIP. Overall E2E regression issues are slowing down the progress.\r\n20-May: HLD work to start, CWC discussion in-progress. On-track, no blockers or issues. Agentforce team is investigating issues Q3 submitted and its not signed-off yet. Q4 testing doesn\u0027t have blockers. Edge rollout (ETA 5/28). There\u0027s no confirmed go-live date right now. The team is also working on a live transcription streaming feature (ETA: 6/8).\r\n13-May: Service Cloud \u0026 Agentforce teams are working on resolving the remaining open issues. GA date Go/no-go decision to be done this wk.\r\n6-May: On-track, no major issues or blockers. Need to have the Epics updated accordingly by the team. Following-up on that.", "id": "a1fEE000000344HYAQ", "name": "[264] Enhanced Chat v2/v1 (Cross Cloud)", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M10 UACP", "program_manager": "Sivaprakasam Ganesan", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-08", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "he