ct status missing", "id": "a1fEE00000034v7YAA", "name": "[264] SMS", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M10 UACP", "program_manager": "Abhisek Dash", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-08", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Testing [264] Toll-free Codes", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "5/1: Active work in progress across dev, testing, and migration planning.\n\nCompleted: Sahil completed core dev \u2014 vendor info storage from m-org and Sinch hardcoding removal (W-22194316, closed). Toll-free testing with Last Mile team completed (W-22194325...", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] [SC] Toll-free code support in UACP SMS", "number": "5"}], "name": "[264] Toll-free Codes"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-08", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Testing [264] Regional Service Expansion", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-01", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "5/1: Vatsal and Arpit raised structured config changes to configure USMS 2.0 connectivity across all FI/FDs. Deployment in progress \\u2014 target completion May 5. Post deployment, Rakesh\\u2019s team to pick up smoke testing and migration activity across...", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] [MC] SMS USMS 2.0 Regional expansion", "number": "4"}], "name": "[264] Regional Service Expansion"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-20", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "5/1: Not yet started. Non-engineering track \u2014 requires legal clearance to enable conversational SMS in countries where DE SMS is blocked but Unified Messaging is supported. No dev lead or legal owner assigned. Needs ownership assignment and legal engagem...", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] [SC] [Non-engg] Legal clearance for conv. SMS in UMA countries", "number": "6"}], "name": "[264] Legal Clearance for Conversational SMS (8 countries)"}], "subcloud": "FY27 SC M10 UACP", "target_release": "264", "theme": "\u26ab Not Prioritized"}, {"health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "Team defining scope and funding ask.", "id": "a1fEE00000036ldYAA", "name": "[264] Unified Setup (Design only)", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M10 UACP", "program_manager": "Swati Deo", "projects": [], "subcloud": "FY27 SC M10 UACP", "target_release": "264", "theme": "-"}, {"health": "Watch", "health_comments": "27-May: BSU ID GA (Compliance Requirement) remains on Watch. Username testing is not yet started. Data model TD still awaiting approval. Q4 perf testing results to be reviewed \u0026 updated.\r\n20-May: Whatsapp Username testing planned this week. E360 WhatsApp team reports blocker is now limited to MoC application work only. BSUID support for Contact, Lead, and Prospect objects remains blocked due to Accounts \u0026 Contacts team bandwidth constraints, uncommitted DMO changes, and Lead/Prospect requirement recently reinstated on 5/15. Service Cloud CCQ team has blitz planned for 5/20 with Q3 testing to follow after deployment to test environments.\r\n13-May: TD dependencies to be sorted out. Discussion ongoing. On-track for Meta GA.\r\n6-May: On-track, need to update the GUS epics accordingly. No blockers.", "id": "a1fEE000000344KYAQ", "name": "[264] WhatsApp Unified Messaging", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M10 UACP", "program_manager": "Sivaprakasam Ganesan", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-08", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Testing [264] Support for Direct Send API (GA)", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-08", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Testing [264] Support for Direct Send API (GA)", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Support Meta WhatsApp Send API in Unified Messaging - GA", "numbe