ents": "6/3 - On watch because there are multiple AFV priorities with target milestone dates in June,July, and August that still require final eng timeline confirmation such as CVS infra connectivity and PSTN Global. 1) CVS Integration, SF CVS Implementation team confirming final requirements w/customer this week, team participating in final security review approval.  2) PSTN Global  - eng team confirming 6/15 delivery date feasibility 3) SC/AFV teams aligned on P0/P1 roadmap priorities, pending PRD and GUS epics for several priorities.\r\n5/26 - On watch because there are multiple AFV priorities with target milestone dates in June,July, and August that still require final eng timeline confirmation such as CVS infra connectivity and PSTN Global. 1) CVS Integration, team participating in deep dive requirements gathering and architecture discussions.  2) PSTN Global  - eng team confirming 6/15 delivery date feasibility 3) SC/AFV teams aligned on P0/P1 roadmap priorities, pending PRD and GUS epics for several prioriries.\r\n5/19 - 1) CVS Integration, team waiting on key milestones and July Pilot scope confirmation from FDEs \u0026 CVS in order to complete e2e plan. Product requirement sessions scheduled for week of 5/19. 2) PSTN Call Forwarding Global: PRD and HLD in progress. Technical solution regarding infra to be used SIP or AFCC and effort estimation/timeline commit due Fri 5/22 by eng team.", "id": "a1fEE00000034LdYAI", "name": "[264] AF Voice", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "program_manager": "Elvi Solanes", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] AFV PSTN Call Forwarding \u2014 Dynamic Routing Service (Core Infrastructure)", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-01", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] AFV PSTN Forward \u2014 Global Expansion Infrastructure (VoiceOps)", "number": "3"}], 