ts progressing well. 1) Admin \u0026 Number Management -completed SKU enforcement. Number-VPOP mapping and number porting automation in progress. 2) Real-time Transcriptions - completed the delete conversation entries API for voice calls in AFCC. Language expansion work underway.\r\n5/13: On-track. \r\n1) Admin \u0026 Number Management - started work on number-VPOP mapping and number porting automation. 2) Real-time Transcriptions - tested the delete conversation entries API for voice calls in AFCC.", "id": "a1fEE000000344ZYAQ", "name": "[264] Admin Setup (incl Number Mgmt), Transcription", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "program_manager": "Sudha Rani Kondapalli", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-04-06", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Perf Testing for [264] Admin and Number Management", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-29", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management- Enforcement CX for new SKUs", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management- Service APIs to support Help Agent", "number": "2"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management- Global Number to VPOP mapping", "number": "2"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-29", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management- Connect APIs for headless number procurement", "number": "3"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management- Voice Number porting automation", "number": "5"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-13", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name":