rted", "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management- SE demo Org. governance", "number": "104"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management- Sandbox Org. Governance", "number": "105"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-20", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management- Default IVR and IVA flows in Salesforce GO", "number": "106"}], "name": "[264] Admin and Number Management"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-04-06", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Perf Testing for [264] Real time Transcriptions", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-06", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q3 End to End Testing for [264] Real time Transcriptions", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-21", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Real time Transcriptions- Delete conversation entries for GDPR compliance", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-20", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[262] Trust - Recording Exporter", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-20", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Real time Transcriptions- Language expansion", "number": "2"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-20", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Trust - Transcriptions Services ( Txn Handler , TTS and  Speech Service )", "number": "3"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Real time Transcriptions- Headless Call Recording \u0026 Transcription Settings", "number": "3"}], "name": "[264] Real time Transcriptions"}], "subcloud": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "target_release": "264", "theme": "\u26ab Not Prioritized"}, {"health": "On Track", "health_comments": "6/2: On-track. 1) Hangup fix validated across performance and Broad Zero environments; deploying to prod.  2) gRPC channel failures - root-caused to a dependency version mismatch; fix in soak validation.\r\n3) Technical debt \u0026 process improvements underway 4) SIP initiation monitoring deferred, pending Opus timeline clarity and further prioritization.\r\n\r\n5/27: On-track. OPUS testing and Hand-up solutioning in progress\r\n\r\n5/20: On-track. IVA project is actively progressing. Splunk dashboard for audio quality tracking is dev-complete. Trust items, automated load testing, and OPUS Q2 testing all in progress. Hang-up mechanism deployed on IVA side, awaiting AFV deployment to test end-to-end\r\n\r\n5/13: On-track. Opus changes completed. Hang-up mechanism between IVA and GSM implementation in progress.", "id": "a1fEE000000344cYAA", "name": "[264] Agentforce Voice \u0026 IVA", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "program_manager": "Sudha Rani Kondapalli", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-04-06", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Perf Testing for [264] IVA", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-------------------------\r\n22 May 2026\r\nWe are picking up things regularly from trust epic along with stories from other epic this is on track.\r\n-------------------------\r\n14 May 2026\r\nWe are picking up things regularly from trust epic along with stories...", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] IVA Trust items", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-------------------------\r\n22 May 2026\r\n1. Implementation completed, IVA Q2 testing complete, 2 bugs raised on agentforce, discussion required with architects for opus params validation\r\n2. E2E testing needs to be coordinated with native and Agentforce t...", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] IVA services layer support for OPUS for WhatsApp", "number": "2"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "Watch", "health_comments": "22 May 2026\r\n1. major implementation complete.\r\n2. feature flag scope changed due to a customer bug, implementation pending for this.\r\n3. FIT tests pending\r\n4. Q2 testing blocked on agentforce deliverable (ETA 27th May)\r\n5. new changes required in design...", "health_status": "Watch", "name": "[264] IVA services layer support for new Hang-up mechanism between IVA and GSM", "number": "3"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Enhanced IVA scale in-line with voice infra scalability", "number": "4"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "22 May 2026\r\n1. Started on implementation, expected to be completed by next week.", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] DTMF Support Over IVA Calls - Native Voice should send DTMF input to AFV", "number": "5"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-13", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q3 End to End Testing for [264] IVA", "number": "21"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-20", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Supv-Transfer to Rep (long term) of AF calls- escalation triggered on AF", "number": "51"}], "name": "[264] IVA"}], "subcloud": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "target_release": "264", "theme": "\u26ab Not Prioritized"}, {"health": "On Track", "health_comments": "5/19 - Program is currently on track overall, with one area to watch. Core foundations for BYOC Direct Connect advanced across carrier onboarding, Media Edge milestones, fraud protection, and Williams Sonoma go-live readiness, though EU rollout and staging face dependency blocks. Regional voice infrastructure progressed well in Frankfurt and Canada, where legacy capacity was successfully retired to make way for the new environment. Additionally, carrier trunk setup for Bandwidth kicked off without blockers, and frontend development for BYOC Number Management is officially underway. Global Regulatory Compliance has been placed on Watch; while caller ID privacy controls moved closer to completion, full lawful intercept activation remains delayed pending budget approval for a third-party Ribbon license.\r\nOn track. Team working with Bandwidth to finalize contract negotiations by 5/22", "id": "a1fEE000000344YYAQ", "name": "[264] Global Expansion (BYO-Carrier) \u0026 Compliance", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "program_manager": "Elvi Solanes", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-04-14", "health": "Unknown", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Canceled", "name": "[264] BYOC - Direct Connect - Admin Exp - Create Trunk Configuration", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-14", "health": "Unknown", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Canceled", "name": "[264] BYOC - Direct Connect - Voice Infra - Telephony Provider Provisioning", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-14", "health": "Unknown", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Canceled", "name": "[264] BYOC - Direct Connect - Voice Infra - Trunk Configuration Provisioning", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-14", "health": "Unknown", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Canceled", "name": "[264] BYOC - Direct Connect - Admin Exp - Manage Trunk Configuration", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-06", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Perf Testing for [264] Bring Your Own Carrier - Direct Connect", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-14", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] BYOC - Direct Connect - Voice Ops - Toggle Media Edge to SBC", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-13", "health": "O