g - dev in progress. 3) CUJ: No updates\r\n\r\n5/26: On-track. 1) Metering \u0026 Billing and Licensing: Dev in progress for 262/264 backport items and Voice Number Lease SKU Enforcement. 2) CUJ: AFCC KAIJU test onboarding artifacts ready with dummy number contract finalized.\r\n\r\n5/20: On-track. Licensing Enablement - Voice Number Lease SKU Enforcement in progress. Metering \u0026 Billing and Critical User Journeys projects - continues development on 262/264 backport work.\r\n\r\n5/11:  On-track. Completed License definitions for Voice SKUs (re-launch) and BYOC SKU. Voice Lease SKU Enforcement in progress. Metering \u0026 Billing and Critical User Journeys continue 262/264 backport development.\r\n\r\n5/5 On-Track - Dev work is in-progress.", "id": "a1fEE000000344eYAA", "name": "[264] Metering and Billing, License Enablement", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "program_manager": "Sudha Rani Kondapalli", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-04-06", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Perf Testing for [264] Licensing Enablement", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-22", "health": "Unknown", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Canceled", "name": "[262/264] Enforcement of Salesforce Voice Usage Credits - IB/OB SKU Purchase", "number": "3"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-29", "health": "Unknown", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Completed", "name": "[262/264] Re-launch Voice Lease and Transport SKUs to support monetization", "number": "4"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-29", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] License Definition for BYO Carrier SKU", "number": "6"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[262/ 264] Enforcement of Salesforce Voice Lease SKU Purchase", "number": "7"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-13", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "