 "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "03/06 : We have reviewed the first level of requirements and filed TD\u0027s. We will put it in our AFCCJuly Priorities List.\r\n\r\n2/27: On hold as per the discussion with Product. UCP is moving towards UACP and any work done towards configuring voice users on ...", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] WhatsApp Voice UCP Support", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] DV - Multiregion VPOP support for Whatsapp + DR", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] DV - WhatsApp Voice BSUID Support", "number": "50"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-20", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] DV - Whatsapp Voice support for BYOC Numbers", "number": "101"}], "name": "[264] Whatsapp Voice"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-04-06", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Perf Testing for [264] WebVoice Support with Multimodal experience", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-13", "health": "Unknown", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Canceled", "name": "Q3 End to End Testing for [264] WebVoice Support with Multimodal experience", "number": "101"}], "name": "[266] WebVoice Support with Multimodal experience"}], "subcloud": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "target_release": "264", "theme": "\u26ab Not Prioritized"}, {"health": "On Track", "health_comments": "06/03/2026 \ud83d\udfe2 On Track: The program is progressing steadily across three active projects. Core scaling, SBC migration, DTMF propagation, multi-vendor webhook ingestion, and Trust epics are all actively executing with no reported blockers. The VPOP Disaster Recovery project has been placed on hold due to competing priorities introduced mid-264. No items currently require exec escalation.\r\n\r\n5/26:Three of four projects are on track \u2014 Scale \u0026 Concurrency (SBC upgrades, DTMF masking, 10K load testing), Native Stack Enhancements (DTMF propagation, multi-vendor webhook ingestion, BSUID testing), and Voice Observability (telemetry, bug fixes in review) \u2014 while VPOP Disaster Recovery (Phase 1) is on hold due to competing AFV priorities introduced mid-264.\r\n5/19  - On Track across all four of its active workstreams.  Scale, Concurrency and Platform Improvements for Native Voice Stack project, which successfully passed its core 10K scaling load tests (UDP/RTP) with 10 of 24 epics actively moving forward and no blockers on its remaining sprints. Foundational work for VPOP Disaster Recovery is on schedule to kick off as soon as the core platform stabilizes, while Voice Observability advanced with one completed epic and ongoing telemetry/diagnostics planning. The Native Stack Enhancements project is progressing smoothly with 4 of its 7 epics\u2014including Native Call Recording, DTMF, Multi-Vendor Webhook, and BSUID\u2014actively under development.", "id": "a1fEE000000344XYAQ", "name": "[264] Voice Infrastructure - Core \u0026 Scale", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M4 AFCC - Voice", "program_manager": "Elvi Solanes", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-06", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Configure Bandwidth SIP and CPS/Concurrency Alerts (Lower + PROD)", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-01", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Dedicated Voice POP for CVS Private Connectivity", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Trust - Godavari [Native Call Recording]", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] WA Voice BSUID Suppor