k", "health_comments": "2nd June\r\n- 264 Go changes fit and finish left and will be completed in 6a sprint\r\n19th May\r\n- Salesforce Go links are not available yet and team is blocked due to unavailability of UX mocks.", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "Salesforce Go Page", "number": "3"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "2nd June\r\n- Team member is working on concierge UX changes and not able to pick up this work in current sprint\r\n19th May\r\n- Team has still not received complete mocks. Able to proceed with current sprint since few mocks were available however still compl...", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "Component Configuration \u0026 Live Preview Panel", "number": "4"}], "name": "[264] Self Service Set-Up"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": null, "health": "Unknown", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "-", "name": "-", "number": "-"}], "name": "[264] Advanced ASA Setup"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "2-Jun-2026: On Track", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Self Service Metering \u0026 Billing", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] Agentforce Self Service Billing \u0026 Packaging", "number": "1"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "- Bug fixes and TF fixes in progress", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] csp-titan trust", "number": "51"}], "name": "[264] Self service billing"}], "subcloud": "FY27 SC M5 Agentic Self Service", "target_release": "264", "theme": "\u26ab Not Prioritized"}, {"health": "On Track", "health_comments": "5/19\r\nCallout -\u003e Citations for Agentforce Actions has been swapped with the GPT-5 migration due to three platform dependencies (TD-0323302, TD-0323303, TD-0323305). Platform will address these in 264, and we\u0027ll uptake the citations work via 264 patches post platform closures.\r\n\r\nBackground: Platform citations currently only work through retrievers. Since AF actions are flow-driven and retriever functionality lacks feature parity, 3 TDs were raised to close this gap.\r\n====\r\nWatch - Agentforce: Platform dependency on Citations for Agentforce Actions: Platform citations only work via retrievers; current AF actions are flow-driven \u0026 retriever functionality lacks feature parity (TDs raised: TD-0323302, TD-0323303, TD-0323305)\r\nImpact: Citations epic to drop from 264; replacement epic (migrating AF Actions to GPT5) being considered\r\nPath to Green: Actively engaging platform team on Citations, GPT5 migration epic queued as a swap\r\nLT Help: None - flagging for visibility.", "id": "a1fEE000000344OYAQ", "name": "[264] Agentfirst IT Service Domain Pack \u0026 Intelligence", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M6 Expand Agentforce IT | HR Service", "program_manager": "Satya Sai Sashi Kumar Bandaru", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q3 End to End Testing for [264] Multi-Agents", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-02", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Perf Testing for [264] Multi-Agents", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] [ITSM] - Employee Agent Development", "number": "1"}], "name": "[264] Multi-Agents"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-04-02", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Perf Testing for [264] Connectors/SCIs/Workflows", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-05-20", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] [ITSM] Request Mgmt - Riverbed Aternity (DEX) connector", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-01", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not 