 "[264] Knowledge Blocks"}], "subcloud": "FY27 SC M7 Deliver Agentic Service Rep Experience - Knowledge", "target_release": "264", "theme": "\u26ab Not Prioritized"}, {"health": "On Track", "health_comments": "5/20: On Track: Update - Execution in progress with assisting customers with onboarding, no callouts\r\n5/5: On Track: Update - Execution is in progress \r\n4/22: On Track: Update - Sprint 1 day 1 as planned started, no callouts \r\n4/15: Update - Team planning completed, LOC in GUS full readiness targeted for 4/17", "id": "a1fEE000000343uYAA", "name": "[264] Self-Learning Knowledge V2", "portfolio": "FY27 SC M7 Deliver Agentic Service Rep Experience - Knowledge", "program_manager": "Valina Kelly", "projects": [{"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-08", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Testing [264] Improve Knowledge Gap Detection By Limiting \u201cNoise\"", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] SLK - Enhancements", "number": "101"}], "name": "[264] Improve Knowledge Gap Detection By Limiting \u201cNoise\""}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-08", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Testing [264] SLK - Improve Evals", "number": "-"}, {"end_date": "2026-04-21", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "[264] Self-Learning Knowledge - Enhance Quality of Gap Detection", "number": "70"}], "name": "[264] SLK - Improve Evals"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-05-08", "health": "Not Started", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "Not Started", "name": "Q4 Testing [264] Deepen the Fidelity of Gap Detection", "number": "-"}], "name": "[264] Deepen the Fidelity of Gap Detection"}, {"epics": [{"end_date": "2026-06-03", "health": "On Track", "health_comments": "-", "health_status": "On Track", "name": "[264] [Condo